Function to run LICA on complete cases

Source: R/flica_completer.R
flica_completer.Rd

This function calls the matlab function to run LICA on complete cases

Usage

flica_completer(ncomp, flica_niter)

Arguments

ncomp

number of components to be used in LICA

flica_niter

number of iterations to be used in LICA

Value

The resulting dataset is the results estimated from LICA

Examples
